When a top-secret laboratory is unexpectedly breached, thousands 
of rampaging raptors are unleashed on Los Angeles! A black-ops unit

chaos. Simultaneously, a truckload of raptors is rerouted to a 
nearby prison. Upon their escape, these ferocious flesh-eaters

smoking hot sorority girls, sinister scientists, muscle-bound 
military and doomed death-row inmates! It's about to get bloody 
in Jurassic City!
